---

<ProductLayout {title} heading="Pergolas & Arbours" {description} {images} {faqs}>
  <div class="text-xl">
    <p>A pergola or arbour adds structure and character to a garden. Whether you want a shaded walkway, a place to sit with climbing plants overhead, or a decorative feature to draw the eye, we'll build one that looks right and lasts.</p>

    <p>We build our pergolas and arbours from solid timber and design them to complement your garden. Climbers, lighting, and decorative detailing can all be incorporated to make the space your own.</p>

    <p>Give us a call on <strong>01228 512303</strong> to discuss what would work best for your garden.</p>

    <h3 class="mt-12 mb-4">What We Offer</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list mb-2">
      <li>Timber and oak pergolas in a range of sizes</li>
      <li>Garden arbours and seating structures</li>
      <li>Designs suited to climbing plants and garden lighting</li>
      <li>Built from solid timber to outlast cheaper alternatives</li>
      <li>Tailored to your garden layout and style</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</ProductLayout>
